cision\", \"from\": 2332, \"to\": 2344}, {\"ngram\": \"the Six Nations\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2372}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There were lots of decisions to make in a short space of time.\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2456, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"lots\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2409}, {\"ngram\": \"decisions\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2422}, {\"ngram\": \"a short space\", \"from\": 2434, \"to\": 2447}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2455}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a lot of commitment, sacrifices and work to be at the best possible level for this team which has given me so much back.\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2464, \"to\": 2469}, {\"ngram\": \"commitment\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2483}, {\"ngram\": \"sacrifices\", \"from\": 2485, \"to\": 2495}, {\"ngram\": \"the best possible level\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2537}, {\"ngram\": \"this team\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2551}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now we have to enjoy it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2610, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It would be wrong to put all of France's success down to Dupont.\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2676, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2645, \"end\": 2651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999993824601093, \"rank\": 6.119207872714735e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dupont\", \"from\": 2669, \"to\": 2675}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Varian Pasquet swung the semi-final against South Africa, Andy Timo was huge in stemming the early Fijian tide in the final and Rayan Rebbadj's goal-kicking was crucial throughout.\", \"from\": 2677, \"to\": 2857, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2678, \"end\": 2684, \"title\": \"http: