 had not won an event on the World Series circuit in 19 years.\", \"from\": 2938, \"to\": 3026, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his arrival\", \"from\": 2947, \"to\": 2958}, {\"ngram\": \"an event\", \"from\": 2977, \"to\": 2985}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Series circuit\", \"from\": 2989, \"to\": 3013}, {\"ngram\": \"19 years\", \"from\": 3017, \"to\": 3025}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With Dupont, they won bronze in his first tournament in Vancouver before claiming gold in Los Angeles a week later.\", \"from\": 3027, \"to\": 3142, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3084, \"end\": 3093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"score\": 0.9500546144747786, \"rank\": 0.05198836296871986, \"text\": \"Vancouver\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vancouver\"}, {\"begin\": 3118, \"end\": 3129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9998722659930235, \"rank\": 0.00012774939011247843, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dupont\", \"from\": 3032, \"to\": 3038}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 3049, \"to\": 3055}, {\"ngram\": \"his first tournament\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3079}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3113}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His third tournament was the SVNS Grand Final, another victory, and now this.\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3221, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3179, \"end\": 3190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_final\", \"score\": 0.9999919670335431, \"rank\": 8.033029864126389e-06, \"text\": \"Grand Final\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_final\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_final\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His third tournament\", \"from\": 3144, \"t